            "icon_alt_text": "Icon Description",
            "icon_title": "Carry <br> a Backpack",
            "icon_description": "You’ll need to carry a backpack weighing 20 to 30 pounds, packed with essential gear for a comfortable trip. Please, be prepared to carry this load while trekking, as the weight will be with you throughout the journey.  The weather can change, with cooler temperatures at higher elevations, so pack layers. Also, pack light, bring only essentials, and maintain a steady pace to balance the load and stay comfortable during the climb.",
