        "section_description": "Mad honey hunting takes place on towering cliffs, a few inches outside the usual comfort zone.  As such, there are a few preparations you'll need to make before you begin the expedition. In this elevation range, drink enough water, wear sturdy footwear, and take it one step at a time for an enjoyable journey.",
