    "basmil_image_text_list_fpDkap": {
      "type": "basmil-image-text-list",
      "blocks": {
        "content_TfCXHJ": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Day 1",
            "description": "<h4>Land to Kathmandu</h4><p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> One-night stay in a 3 Star Hotel</p><p>When you arrive at TIA (Tribhuwan Intl Airport), our team will arrange a convenient airport pickup and drop-off service to your hotel. On the same day, we’ll give you a clear and helpful briefing about your upcoming travel plans.</p><p>After that, we’ll make sure you enjoy a delicious meal to end the day on a satisfying note. We look forward to seeing you refreshed and ready for the next exciting days of your honey hunting expedition.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": "",
            "image_type": "svg",
            "image_alt": "Mad Honey",
            "svg": "day1",
            "image_width": "87.126%",
            "svg_style": "aspect-ratio:\n757.13 / 263.94;\nmargin:0 auto;"
          }
        },
        "content_z8RLbD": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Day 2",
            "description": "<h3>Kathmandu to Besisahar</h3><p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> One-night stay in a 3 Star Hotel</p><p>After breakfast, we go on to the captivating panorama of Besisahar, Lamjung.<br/>As the dawn greets you with its golden rays, we start our beautiful landscapes of a small idyllic village. Our trusty van will be ready to take you on this scenic adventure. <strong> </strong></p><p>You will witness a great deal of scenic beauty that greets you on its way. Along the way, you will delight in observing the majesty of rolling rivers and snow-capped mountains painting the horizon.</p><p>In the afternoon, we will serve a delicious lunch from a selection of menu options. After reaching the serene haven of Besisahar, surrounded by nature’s loving arms,<strong> </strong>we'll treat you to tasty snacks and a satisfying dinner.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": "",
            "image_type": "svg",
            "image_alt": "Mad Honey",
            "svg": "day2",
            "image_width": "82.94%",
            "svg_style": "aspect-ratio:720.75/272.03;\nmargin:0 auto;"
          }
        },
        "content_8mzNtY": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Day 3",
            "description": "<h3>Besisahar to Honey Hunting Village</h3><h3> </h3><p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> One-night stay in a community homestay</p><p>The day begins with a delectable breakfast served in the hotel, filling us with energy for the exciting adventures ahead. We get ready for the place closest to the thrill and excitement, eagerly anticipating the experiences that await us.</p><p>Later, we’ll enjoy a delicious lunch at a community homestay, savoring local flavors and immersing ourselves in the region’s food culture. As we explore, we’ll have the unique chance to observe the locals’ preparations and their lively gatherings in anticipation of tomorrow’s event.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": "",
            "image_type": "svg",
            "image_alt": "Mad Honey",
            "svg": "day3",
            "image_width": "34.5%",
            "svg_style": "aspect-ratio:299.78/272.03;\nmargin:0 auto;"
          }
        },
        "content_HUUEJL": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Day 4",
            "description": "<h3>Night Stay at a hotel in Besisahar</h3><h3> </h3><p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> Night Stay at a hotel in Besisahar</p><p>A hearty breakfast will be served at the homestay, offering a limited but satisfying selection of food options. After a short briefing about the upcoming trials and challenges we may encounter, our team ensures that we have the right gear and prioritizes our safety throughout the journey.</p><p>As the sun rises, we go on our adventure to the mad honey hunting site, which is a pleasant half-hour to 45-minute walk from the homestay. Along the way, we are treated to the sight of cascading waterfalls and breathtaking mountain ranges, enhancing the scenic beauty of our trek.</p><p>Upon reaching the site, we witness the thrilling process of honey hunting, which lasts for around 4 to 5 hours. You’ll even have the chance to taste the <a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/\">fresh mad honey</a> directly from the hive while enjoying snacks provided during the wait.</p><p>Once we have experienced this unique activity, we make our way back to the community homestay for a well-deserved lunch. Later in the day, we return to Besisahar, where we spend the night in a comfortable hotel. For dinner, we conveniently dine in the same hotel for a pleasant end to a fulfilling day of adventure.</p><p>After a rewarding day of honey hunting, we say our farewells to this unforgettable expedition.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": "",
            "image_type": "svg",
            "image_alt": "Mad Honey",
            "svg": "day4",
            "image_width": "34.5%",
            "svg_style": "aspect-ratio:299.78/272.03;\nmargin:0 auto;"
          }
        },
        "content_6MJGE8": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Day 5",
            "description": "<h3>Besisahar to Kathmandu</h3><h3> </h3><p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> One-night stay at 3-Star Hotel</p><p>The next day, after enjoying a delicious breakfast, we will begin our journey back to Kathmandu. Along the way, we will stop for a satisfying lunch, either in Muglin or at a convenient spot on the route.  Once we reach our destination, we will ensure a smooth drop-off at your hotel.<strong> </strong>To round off your trip with comfort, we will take care of your last meal, ensuring you have a satisfying dining experience. We will handle all arrangements for your hotel accommodation.  </p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": "",
            "image_type": "svg",
            "image_alt": "Mad Honey",
            "svg": "day5",
            "image_width": "74.68%",
            "svg_style": "aspect-ratio:\n649.05/\n272.03;\nmargin:0 auto;"
          }
        }
      },
