            "heading": "Day 1",
            "subheading": "Land to Kathmandu",
            "paragraph": "<p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> One-night stay in a 3 Star Hotel</p><p>When you arrive at TIA (Tribhuwan Intl Airport), our team will arrange a convenient airport pickup and drop-off service to your hotel. On the same day, we’ll give you a clear and helpful briefing about your upcoming travel plans.<br/><br/>After that, we’ll make sure you enjoy a delicious meal to end the day on a satisfying note. We will spend enough time making you feel welcomed and connected in this foreign land, the remaining part of the day is then all yours. We look forward to seeing you refreshed and ready for the next exciting days of your honey hunting expedition.</p>",
