            "paragraph": "<p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> One-night stay at 3-Star Hotel</p><p>The next day, after enjoying a delicious breakfast, we will begin our journey back to Kathmandu. Along the way, we will stop for a satisfying lunch, either in Muglin or at a convenient spot on the route.  <br/><br/>Once we reach our destination, we will ensure a smooth drop-off at your hotel. To round off your trip with comfort, we will take care of your last meal, ensuring you have a satisfying dining experience. We will handle all arrangements for your hotel accommodation. This is the day when we bid farewell, don't forget to leave your feedbacks to help us identify areas for improvement!</p>",
