      "settings": {
        "heading_title": "Gear List",
        "heading_description": "<p>Stay comfortable on your honey hunting expedition by choosing the right essentials for your backpack. By using versatile layers that can be easily combined, you can achieve optimal comfort without carrying excessive weight. These layers provide the perfect balance of insulation, ventilation, and weather protection to adapt to changing conditions.</p>",
