        "heading_description": "<p>Have questions about the gear list? We’re here to help! Feel free to give us a call at <strong>+977 9849388031</strong>, and our knowledgeable team will provide you with the answers you need. For any other information to assist you in preparing for your trip, reach out to us on WhatsApp. Don’t hesitate to get in touch with us today!</p>",
